  <h2>Oshie Overview</h2>
  <p>Oshie is a Learning Management System (LMS) used by organizations of all sizes
    to deploy and operate their classes, lessons, and educational materials .
    Our platform allows organizations to focus on their educational goals and
    strategies while Oshie focuses on infrastructure management, scaling, and security.
    Oshie applies security best practices and manages platform security so
    customers can focus on their business. Our platform is designed to protect
    customers from threats by applying security controls at every layer from
    physical to application, isolating customer applications and data, and with
    its ability to rapidly deploy security updates without customer interaction
    or service interruption.</p>

